-- Esther Gordillo Re-elected Head of Mexico Teacher Union: Milenio
-- B y   B e n   B a i n
-- 2012-10-20T21:24:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-20/esther-gordillo-re-elected-head-of-mexico-teacher-union-milenio.html
Mexican teachers’ union head Elba Esther Gordillo was re-elected for another six years, Milenio
 newspaper reported .  Esther Gordillo was elected by 98 percent of the delegates
who voted at the union’s convention in the resort town of
Cancun.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ben Bain in Mexico City at 
 bbain2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
